PyObject* pyInstance_dsect ( ResourceRef &  rr  ) 

Returns a Python object that wraps the resource reference.

Note the new python object returned will hold another reference to the resource, thus you must release the python reference and the resource reference to free the object.

Parameters:
rr The loaded resource.
Returns:
Python version of the ResourceRef.
